item.title: Codes codes! help!
item.dc:creator: @MisterZ MisterZ
item.description:
@MisterZ wrote:

Go to www.codefasga.com for all your ID’s or you can look up IDs on the moparscape client from the help menu.

You add all the info in autospawn.cfg to add npc’s. To add item drops go to npchandler.java and you add your item drop and the npc in there. To make random item drops you do this in one of the item.java files most people use item2.java. If you don’t get that I can chop it down for you…
